Package duke.command

Interface Command

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddCommand, AddDeadlineCommand, AddEventCommand, AddTodoCommand, DeleteCommand, DoneCommand, ExitCommand, FindCommand, ListCommand, RemindCommand, ScheduleCommand
    public interface Command
    This is an abstraction over the commands entered by the user. All commands that implements the Command interface will have to override the execute method.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

    • Method Detail

      • execute

        java.lang.String execute​(TaskManager taskManager,
                         UserInterface ui,
                         Storage storage)
                  throws InvalidParameterException
        Executes the command.
        Parameters:
        taskManager - the task manager for the tasks
        ui - the user interface
        storage - the storage for the taskManager
        Returns:
        a string representation of the output after command execution
        Throws:
        InvalidParameterException - if the parameters passed into the command are invalid
